Package: DR2S
Title: Dual redundant reference sequencing
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Gerhard Schöfl <gerhard.schofl@gmail.com>
Description: Generate highly accurate reference sequences from heterozygous
    HLA and KIR samples by combining data from long-read and short-read
    sequencing technologies
